nd care. This facility features modern training facilities, experienced and certified staff, offering pet care....\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Seattle\",\"addressRegion\":\"WA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":5,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/all-the-best-pet-care-lake-city\",\"name\":\"All The Best Pet Care - Lake City\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/all-the-best-pet-care-lake-city\",\"description\":\"All The Best Pet Care - Lake City has become the premier destination for Seattle dog owners. This facility features climate-controlled facilities for Washington's rainy climate, caring and attentive...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Seattle\",\"addressRegion\":\"WA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":6,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/eastside-dog-and-cats-too\",\"name\":\"Eastside Dog and Cats Too\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/eastside-dog-and-cats-too\",\"description\":\"Among Seattle's top-rated facilities, Eastside Dog and Cats Too excels in year-round care. This facility features heated spaces for comfortable year-round play, experienced and certified staff,...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Seattle\",\"addressRegion\":\"WA\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":7,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/the-seattle-barkery\",\"name\":\"The Seattle Barkery\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/the-seattle-barkery\",\"description\":\"Washington pet parents in Seattle choose The Seattle Barkery for premium care. This facility features climate-controlled facilities for Washington's rainy climate, experienced and certified staff,...\",\"address\":{\"@type\"